## Data License

The food composition data included in this project is sourced from the
"Standard Tables of Food Composition in Japan" (日本食品標準成分表)
published by the Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and
Technology (MEXT), Japan.

This data is available under the Government of Japan Standard Terms of Use
(Version 2.0), which is compatible with Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International (CC BY 4.0).

Attribution: 文部科学省「日本食品標準成分表（八訂）増補2023年」
